{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ac678498-3dbd-461d-8155-98ddb86e4fd1", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac678498-3dbd-461d-8155-98ddb86e4fd1@1.pkg/1772597671978/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597672923", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac678498-3dbd-461d-8155-98ddb86e4fd1@1.pkg/1772597671978/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597672923"}, "identifier": "ac678498-3dbd-461d-8155-98ddb86e4fd1", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查做更好自己的要求。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div>\n<p align=\"justify\">②④：依据教材知识，分析题文，面对小丽觉得“累”的状况，我们应鼓励她学会接纳自己，包括优点和缺点，并在此基础上不断追求自我提升。同时，善于向他人和各种资源学习，借鉴经验以完善自己，故②④符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">①：既要欣赏他人，也要欣赏自己的长处和优势，接纳自己的不足，而非掩饰不足，故①说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③：金无足赤，人无完人，不可能做到完美，故③说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">故本题选C。</p>\n</div>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p align=\"justify\">（改编）初中生小丽总是拿自己和别人进行比较。有时候为自己的优秀成绩感到骄傲，但有时候又羡慕别人有许多特长。总是与别人比较让她觉得很累。面对小丽的“累”，你想对她说（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">①欣赏他人的长处和优势，掩饰自己的不足</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②学会接纳自己的全部，向更好的方向发展</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③学会不断挖掘自己的潜能，做完美的自己</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">④善于向他人、课本、社会学习，完善自己</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "label": "", "title": "（改编）初中生小丽总是拿自己和别人进行比较。有时候为自己的优秀成绩感到骄傲，但有时候又羡慕别人有许多特长。总是与别人比较让她觉得很累。面对小丽的“累”，你想对她说（   ）①欣赏他人的长处和优势，掩饰自己的不足②学会接纳自己的全部，向更好的方向发展③学会不断挖掘自己的潜能，做完美的自己④善于向他人、课本、社会学习，完善自己 ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac678498-3dbd-461d-8155-98ddb86e4fd1@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754973229876", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p align=\"justify\">①④</p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">①③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">②④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p align=\"justify\">（改编）初中生小丽总是拿自己和别人进行比较。有时候为自己的优秀成绩感到骄傲，但有时候又羡慕别人有许多特长。总是与别人比较让她觉得很累。面对小丽的“累”，你想对她说（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">①欣赏他人的长处和优势，掩饰自己的不足</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">②学会接纳自己的全部，向更好的方向发展</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">③学会不断挖掘自己的潜能，做完美的自己</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">④善于向他人、课本、社会学习，完善自己</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$